data.description: VERY MOTIVATED! A beautiful quaint home in a very quiet and safe subdivision that has so much to offer. This home has the feel of being out in the woods but very centrally located between four towns. (Blue Ridge Ga.,Blairsville Ga.,  Copperhill Tn. & Murphy N.C.... Come and enjoy sitting on the front porch, back screened in porch or by the firepit with the peace and quiet of nature and  watching plenty of wildlife running around. The home offers three bedrooms with two baths with additional plumbing for a third bathroom in the basement along with an option for a 3rd bedroom. The workshop in the basement is great for someone that likes to do projects.
